# Superpowers Skills

Superpowers is installed at `~/.cursor/plugins/superpowers/skills/`. Before any task, check whether a skill applies and read it using the Read tool at that path.

## Skill Index

| Skill | Path | Trigger |
|-------|------|---------|
| `brainstorming` | `~/.cursor/plugins/superpowers/skills/brainstorming/SKILL.md` | Before writing ANY code — refine requirements first |
| `writing-plans` | `~/.cursor/plugins/superpowers/skills/writing-plans/SKILL.md` | After brainstorming — create a detailed implementation plan |
| `test-driven-development` | `~/.cursor/plugins/superpowers/skills/test-driven-development/SKILL.md` | During implementation — RED-GREEN-REFACTOR always |
| `systematic-debugging` | `~/.cursor/plugins/superpowers/skills/systematic-debugging/SKILL.md` | When debugging any bug or unexpected behaviour |
| `verification-before-completion` | `~/.cursor/plugins/superpowers/skills/verification-before-completion/SKILL.md` | Before declaring something fixed |
| `subagent-driven-development` | `~/.cursor/plugins/superpowers/skills/subagent-driven-development/SKILL.md` | When executing a multi-task plan |
| `executing-plans` | `~/.cursor/plugins/superpowers/skills/executing-plans/SKILL.md` | Batch execution with human checkpoints |
| `dispatching-parallel-agents` | `~/.cursor/plugins/superpowers/skills/dispatching-parallel-agents/SKILL.md` | When tasks can run concurrently |
| `requesting-code-review` | `~/.cursor/plugins/superpowers/skills/requesting-code-review/SKILL.md` | Before submitting a PR or finishing a branch |
| `receiving-code-review` | `~/.cursor/plugins/superpowers/skills/receiving-code-review/SKILL.md` | When responding to review feedback |
| `using-git-worktrees` | `~/.cursor/plugins/superpowers/skills/using-git-worktrees/SKILL.md` | After design approval — isolate work on a new branch |
| `finishing-a-development-branch` | `~/.cursor/plugins/superpowers/skills/finishing-a-development-branch/SKILL.md` | When all tasks are complete — merge/PR/discard decision |
| `writing-skills` | `~/.cursor/plugins/superpowers/skills/writing-skills/SKILL.md` | When creating a new skill |
| `using-superpowers` | `~/.cursor/plugins/superpowers/skills/using-superpowers/SKILL.md` | Introduction and meta-guide to the skills system |

## Mandatory Rules

- **If there is even a 1% chance a skill applies — read it.** This is not optional.
- **Brainstorm before coding.** Never jump straight to implementation.
- **TDD always.** Write a failing test first, then make it pass.
- **Systematically debug.** No guessing; follow the 4-phase process.
- **Verify before declaring done.** Evidence over claims.

## If the Plugin Is Missing

If `~/.cursor/plugins/superpowers/` doesn't exist, reinstall with `/plugin-add superpowers` in Cursor Agent chat, or run:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/obra/superpowers.git ~/.cursor/plugins/superpowers
```
